<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Texting.jpg" class="image" title="A user typing a text message on an LG enV"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/86/Texting.jpg/180px-Texting.jpg" width="180" height="120" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Texting.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
A user typing a text message on an <a href="/wiki/LG_enV" title="LG enV" class="mw-redirect">LG enV</a></div>
